## My Cats [/cats{?page,size}]
### Get all cat sightings [GET]

+ Parameters
    + page: 1 (number, required) page number
    + size: 10 (number, required) - page size
+ Request

    + Header 
    
                Authorization: Basic dXNlcjpwYXNzd29yZA==
                x-api-version: 1.0
    
