## Create a new Cat [/cats]
### Create a cat sighting [POST]

+ Request

    + Header
    
            Authorization: Basic dXNlcjpwYXNzd29yZA==
            Content-type: application/json
            x-api-version: 1.0
    
    + Body

            {
                "sightedAt" : "2014-08-29T07:10",
                "imageUrl" : "https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/uid-19247681/201408/14562881209_046a7f4d3d_z.jpg",
                "description" : "Another cat I saw on the bush",
                "tags": [
                    "stripy"
                ]
            }
        
+ Response 201 

    + Header
    
            Location : cats/abbd4122

## One of my Cat sightings [/cats/{id}]
### Get a Cat sighting [GET]

+ Parameters
    + id: `aba443c` (string, required) - `id` of the spider sighting
    
+ Request

    + Header
    
            Authorization: Basic dXNlcjpwYXNzd29yZA==
            x-api-version: 1.0
        
+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Header
    
            ETag : "euyfewuyfvew76f7"
            cache-control: max-age=600
            
    + Body

            {
                "sightedAt" : "2014-08-29T07:00",
                "imageUrl" : "https://s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/uid-19247681/201408/14562881209_046a7f4d3d_z.jpg",
                "description" : "Spider I saw on the train",
                "tags": [
                    "stripy"
                ]
            }
            
            
### Update a cats sighting [PUT]

+ Parameters
    + id: `aba443c` (string, required) - `id` of the spider sighting
    
+ Request

    + Header
    
            Authorization: Basic dXNlcjpwYXNzd29yZA==
            Content-type: application/json
            x-api-version: 1.0
            
    + Body
    
            {
                "sightedAt" : "2014-08-29T07:15",
                "description" : "No, it was definitely different"
            }
        
+ Response 200